These functions are designed to mimic their scipy counterparts.

https://docs.scipy.org/doc/scipy/reference/generated/scipy.stats.mstats.linregress.html#linregress
https://docs.scipy.org/doc/scipy/reference/generated/scipy.stats.pearsonr.html#pearsonr
https://docs.scipy.org/doc/scipy/reference/generated/scipy.stats.spearmanr.html#spearmanr
